            <article class="initiative-card">
              <h4>Identity Continuity Frameworks</h4>
              <p>
                Developing structured approaches to preserve personal identity across stages of cognitive change. Our frameworks integrate narrative methods, sensory cues, and relational mapping to create a holistic picture of personhood that endures beyond memory.
              </p>
            </article>

            <article class="initiative-card">
              <h4>Family Caregiver Support Models</h4>
              <p>
                Researching best practices for caregiver education, resilience, and community connection. We study the emotional, logistical, and social dimensions of caregiving to develop support models that reduce burnout and strengthen family bonds.
              </p>
            </article>

            <article class="initiative-card">
              <h4>Technology-Assisted Care Tools</h4>
              <p>
                Exploring how technology can augment human-centered care without replacing human connection. From digital memory archives to adaptive communication aids, we develop tools that serve people &mdash; not the other way around.
              </p>
            </article>

          </div>

